★BOARD The board is a 4×4 matrix where all the pieces get placed .
★PIECES There are 16 pieces in total , each with 4 details that make them unique . The pieces differ in : •Color : beige , brown •Shape : circle , square •Size : short , tall •Fill : hole , no hole
★MOVES Each player can choose where to place a piece , but the piece he gets to place is chosen by the opponent . At the beginning of the game players can choose who is going to move first . •first player • second player •take turns At first the turn will be of the opponent , so he can choose the piece that is going to be placed . Player 1 0 wainting... Player 2 0 choose a piece for player 1
★WINNER The winner is the player who is the last to put a piece on the board , and make a line of four pieces that share a common detail . Pieces can be in a line that is : •horizontal •vertical •diagonal
